long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension solves Sudoku puzzles using cutting edge Sudoku-Solving-Technology.  Puzzles can be solved with a single click when visiting sites from the "supported sites" list.  If a site is unsupported, the puzzle can be passed to the solver manually using the "manual input" option.
